# Terraform
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Sensitive / generated at runtime by the workflow (never commit these)
**/terraform.auto.tfvars
**/nonsecret.auto.tfvars

# Cross-pass handoff files from scripts/setup-auth.sh (one holds a live
# client secret — never commit these)
scripts/.setup-auth-host
scripts/.setup-auth-creds

# Terraform lock file is fine to commit; uncomment to ignore if you prefer
# .terraform.lock.hcl

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
